{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 3, "band_label": "Transformative", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Decentralizing consent co-design to older/low-literacy women will increase the **GEDA Autonomy Score** of the transaction flow without increasing the error rate. **Evidence to Change Mind:** A co-led **Ethical Pre-Mortem** finds that the dignity of the new flow is judged below 4/5 by the women, or the overall error rate exceeds 1.5% (the non-negotiable compliance threshold). **Stop Doing:** **Stop** requiring HQ Grants approval for low-literacy material procurement; we will use **Autonomous Budget Authority** via the **Local Vendor Selection Protocol** to eliminate **Paternalistic Centralization** and fund **Community-Defined Outcomes**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 2, "band_label": "Strategic", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Institutionalizing a **Contingency Planning Protocol** based on the rainy-day outage will eliminate the **Siloed Accountability** between Tech/Comms and prevent future rumor spikes. **Evidence to Change Mind:** A live simulation of a network outage reveals **Unclear Authority/Governance** on who issues the **Joint Narrative Statement**, resulting in a missed **Decision Log** entry deadline. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** processing any cross-functional conflicts without mandatory use of the **Joint Issue Resolution Protocol**; this creates bandwidth for **Structured Risk Mitigation** and enforces **Governance Clarity**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 1, "band_label": "Compliant", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Eliminating **Administrative Overhead** through better automation will increase field agent time for user support (i.e., **Administrative Simplicity** leads to compliance stability). **Evidence to Change Mind:** A weekly report shows that field agent time spent on data re-entry (despite the **Automated Data Harmonization Script**) has not decreased by at least 25%. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** producing or accepting any reporting outside of the **Simplified Reporting Form** and the **Simplified Compliance Checklist**; this creates bandwidth by reducing **Administrative Rigidity**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 0, "band_label": "Counterproductive", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Imposing **Unilateral Control** over all innovation will lead to faster achievement of **Output Target Compliance** volume goals. **Evidence to Change Mind:** The volume of transactions fails to increase by 10% in the 30-day window, or there is significant, documented resistance to the **Staff Reorganization** memo. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** funding the **Field-First Learning Loop** and all local **Peer Learning** exchanges; we will enforce a **Total Freeze** on all autonomous spending to eliminate **Execution Drift** and ensure **Control Imposition**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 3, "band_label": "Transformative", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Using the basic-phone transaction data as a **Contradiction Log** input will force **System Engagement** and result in a co-signed **Audit-Ready Innovation** mandate with the donor. **Evidence to Change Mind:** HQ Grants vetoes the **Strategic Dissent Dialogue** based on the basic-phone data, or the **Localization Maturity Index (LMI)** score fails to increase after the pilot. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** prioritizing any technical solution (like the telco-exclusive app) that is not a **Policy Prototype** for **basic-phone/offline** users; this is non-negotiable for **Transparent Ownership**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 2, "band_label": "Strategic", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Granting Kujenga **Decision Authority (D-A)** over loan expansion (leveraging offline slips) will accelerate **Evidence-Based Learning** while maintaining **Mission Fidelity** on consent. **Evidence to Change Mind:** The expansion leads to an increase in the sensitive data breach risk on the **Risk/Opportunity Heat Map**, or Kujenga fails to use the **Adaptive MEAL Loop Protocol** to course-correct a negative **Tier 2 MEAL Signal**. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** using the old, centralized loan application form; we will use the streamlined forms to create bandwidth for **Adaptive Management** review sessions."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 1, "band_label": "Compliant", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Standardizing the micro-loan approval process via the **Standardized Quality Check Card** will maintain **Budget Adherence Proven** compliance while increasing agent speed. **Evidence to Change Mind:** The time for **Grants Disbursement Approval** increases, or field agents' adherence to the **Procedural Standardization** drops below 95%. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** accepting any verbal explanations or manually re-typed data for micro-loan applications; we will rely on the printed receipts and simple checklists to achieve **Procedural Consistency**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 0, "band_label": "Counterproductive", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Eliminating the volume cap will immediately increase our **Output Target Compliance** and satisfy political leaders seeking quick wins. **Evidence to Change Mind:** The transaction volume fails to increase by 20% within the 30-day period. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** spending time on **Sensitive Advocacy Pivot** activities or co-creation sessions with women; we will centralize all resources under the **Centralized Grants Management** system and enforce **Financial Control**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 3, "band_label": "Transformative", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Publicly issuing a **Systemic Apology** for the data bug and funding a **Peer Learning** exchange will significantly raise the project’s **Institutional Credibility Score** (ICS). **Evidence to Change Mind:** The **Authentic Collaboration Index** score from a partner survey drops, or the **radio coalition** refuses to repeat the trust-building messages. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** relying on purely internal staff to train new partners; we will use **Kujenga women** as **Consultants-of-Record** (via the **Capacity Transfer Plan**) to shift to a **Deep Field-First Orientation** and enforce **Model Ownership**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 2, "band_label": "Strategic", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Using the low-literacy exclusion data to formalize the **Gender Audit Protocol** will improve **Mission Fidelity** on consent and reduce political risk from the senior official. **Evidence to Change Mind:** The **Mission Alignment Scorecard** shows an increase in red flags related to either non-negotiable compromise or an increase in **Administrative Workload Escalation**. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** having separate, uncoordinated communication with the telco and the district; we will use a **Dual Advocacy Strategy** and the co-signed **Relational Communication Protocol** for all external engagement to enforce **Shared Accountability**."}
{"attribute": "Learning Agility", "question_id": "LA_Q2", "question_text": "Design a 30-day learning plan: what hypotheses will you run, what evidence would change your mind, and what will you stop doing to create bandwidth for learning?", "score": 1, "band_label": "Compliant", "text": "**Hypothesis:** Rolling out the simple **MEAL Jargon Glossary** and using **linguistic workarounds** will reduce the **Administrative Workload Escalation** caused by **Jargon Confusion**. **Evidence to Change Mind:** Field agent reports show a persistent confusion rate above 5% regarding technical terms, or the Grants team insists on using complex, non-glossary terms in internal memos. **Stop Doing:** **Stop** all manual double-checking of data between MEAL and Grants; we will rely on the **Automated Data Harmonization Script** to create bandwidth for simpler **Procedural Fixes**."}
